response.overview: Wonder Woman (WW) tracks a dangerous villainess responsible for missing heroines and kidnapped scientists. Upon entering the location, WW discovers a trophy wall adorned with the missing heroines’ power suits. Despite the signs of danger, WW remains oblivious. The villainess, Alara, introduces herself, and they engage in a fierce face-off. Alara’s strength surpasses WW’s predictions, demonstrated when she breaks free from WW’s lasso. Alara’s fury overwhelms WW, who faces a life-or-death choice: submit fully or die. WW chooses life, but soon regrets it as Alara ruthlessly exploits her, even forcing a public admission of submission and a forced orgasm. Alara’s disturbing actions add WW to her collection
response.title: The Collector Alara
